data.description: CALLING ALL INVESTORS!! ADD THIS GREAT HOME TO YOUR PORTFOLIO!! Investment opportunity in Enderly Park. Neighborhood has some new construction and nice renovations. Near uptown Charlotte, local favorites, and the Bank of America Stadium. Extensive driveway to accomodate lots of vehicles. Original home was a 2BR, 1BA. Per sellers, the dining room/sunroom was grandfathered in as HLA even though the ceiling height is slightly under 7ft, but we have that room listed as additional living area. The den, primary bedroom and primary bath were all added by the sellers and could be considered a 2nd living quarters. Den, Primary Bedroom and Primary bath are all heated and cooled making them HLA, but are not accessible without going through the dining room/sunroom. Sellers received a Certificate of Occupancy from the county for that area when it was completed. Meaurements in the attachments. Sellers are MOTIVATED!
